Example of standalone spam daemon with two spam engines:
	KAS engine and spamassasin.


README
-----------
* to generate 'configure' script 'autoreconf --force --install'
* to make debug build: './configure CFLAGS="-g3 -O0 -Wall"'
* to make debug build: './configure --enable-debug-mode
* to use Makefile.ia32 on Debian Squeeze:
  sudo apt-get install ia32-libs-gtk
  cd /lib32 ; ln -s libglib-2.0.so.0.2400.2 libglib-2.0.so
  cd /usr/lib32 ; ln -s libgthread-2.0.so.0.2400.2 libgthread-2.0.so

